style.css:
@-moz-document url-prefix("http://www1.flightrising.com/"), url-prefix("http://www.flightrising.com/") {
#dragon-image-box {
    background-image: url("http://flightrising.com/images/layout/trans.png"), /* replace with skin or accent url*/
                      url("http://flightrising.com/images/layout/trans.png"), /* replace with second skin or accent url*/
                      url("http://flightrising.com/images/layout/trans.png") !important;  /*replace with a scry url*/
}

/*

- From the dressing room, select the mannequin of the scry's breed and gender and apply an invisibility cloak to get clothing to show up correctly.

- If you want to remove a skin/accent or scry without replacing it with a different one, you can replace the url with random text or a transparent image (ex: 'none' or 'http://flightrising.com/images/layout/trans.png') when you want to stop dressing scries, either replace all URLS with none/transparent or disable the addon.

- You can find skin/accent URLs on items.kanojo.de.

- If the scry isn't showing up properly, make sure you've hit Save and that the Enabled tickbox is still checked (if you hit Edit while it's disabled, it can be a bit finnicky and un-enable when you save.)

*/

}
